highlights.text: “Espresso” by Sabrina Carpenter is the highest new entry on Top Songs USA at #4.
“When It Rains It Pours” by Luke Combs is the biggest gainer on Top Songs USA, up 72 spots at #127.
Future has the most spots on Top Songs USA. “Like That” is the highest at #2.
“No Role Modelz” by J. Cole has been on Top Songs USA the longest, at 204 weeks straight.
